Another entry in the <a href="https://www.kenblanchardbooks.com/books/" target="_blank"></b>The One Minute Manager</b></a> library series by Ken Blanchard. Another valuable contribution to the body of knowledge of those aspiring to become effective managers, and therefore, team leaders.

Today's leader must be an enabler of people and a facilitator of teams. "We need managers who can focus the group's attention and enthusiasm on continuous improvement."

What is most often overlooked is the teams stage of development. The process of devloping a high performing team involves three skills: 

~ Diagnosis
~ Adaptablility
~ Empowerment








